values:
or does it feel like sometimes people think i'm a bajillionaire?

EVERY and ANYtime someone wants to hang out.... I have to drive an hour to do so... this is a LOT of gas... Gas... is $4 a gallon... I... have no money.. That's pretty much my life story.. but I do it.. anytime someone wants to hang out. So can I just PLEASE point out that it's a drive for me and I don't really have the gas to do it..&nbsp;

just so you're aware..&nbsp;&nbsp;

I'm not trying to be bitchy.. I just wanna make you aware because I know noone ever thinks about it. I know.. EVERYONE but me is in the same city.. but it's not my fault!! I have no control over where I live. And I want to move to Indy.. but I can't really afford it right now.I can't afford a house payment alone.

So it's getting warmer now.. so I just want to advertise... that my house is real fun when it's warm! and I live only like.. 20 min away from Edinburg mall.. which is always fun. and people should want to come hang out here sometime. just saying. to let you know. it's hard for me to get there all the time. j2lyk. but I love you all to death. i'm just having an annoying day. and i thought about this.but I have to go to bed now.. so i can get up and drive alllll the way to school.... then allll the way into indy to only hang out with kristi a lil =( and Nick a lot =] because I won't be seeing him enough over the next week! ahah.&nbsp; But Kristi and I aren't gonna get very much time and that's lameo. and Nick and I are FINALLY gonna see No Country For Old Men!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! we've been waiting since before it even came out.. it kinda came out the same time as Lars... so maybe!!!!! Lars and the Real Girl will be coming out soon!!! .. I just got my hopes up.. bad idea.
